Detailed Description

Implementation of BasicInterval.

Abstract interface for interval domains.

Author:
Frederic Py <fpy@mbari.org>

This file defines the bases class for implementing interval domains in TREX. It offers multiple utilities to have unified access/input/output for this kind of domain.
